Send one output as input to other
symbol == > : overwrite
symbol == >> : append
FileDescriptor = 0 : stdin : standard input 
FileDescriptor = 1 : stdout : standard output
FileDescriptor = 2 : stderr : standard error

Merge Multiple Files Content in Single File {
cat file1 file2 >> file3
}

Extract Relevent data from one file into other file {
grep ReleventExpression file1name >> filename
}

Standard Error : when command gives error {
    command 2>> filename : redirect error only
    command &>> filename : redirect error or output
}

